{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 1945, "height": 2641, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [120, 703, 196, 1371], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三八三", "block_bbox": [126, 2000, 176, 2115], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "邑生员杜星五撰文并书丹\n本村以及西坡共珍\n\n时嘉庆十七年岁次壬申一阳月\n", "block_bbox": [373, 238, 905, 403], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "永垂不朽", "block_bbox": [375, 479, 545, 521], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "钦赐耆老杜公讳廷学之墓", "block_bbox": [375, 539, 830, 583], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "image", "block_content": "茶\n\n，嗜\n\n同，侄\n\n后迁后\n\n皇\n\n", "block_bbox": [1224, 380, 1744, 2424], "block_id": 5, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "修德承继。公卒，祖茔地狭，同葬于此，是为记。", "block_bbox": [290, 600, 1330, 764], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "道光陆年岁次丙戌夏月吉日立", "block_bbox": [374, 782, 907, 823], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "清故处士杜公讳金龙配氏墓", "block_bbox": [376, 902, 884, 942], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "寨，及杜金龙事迹等）\n", "block_bbox": [293, 963, 1329, 1064], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "陕郡增生□□口□口顿首拜□邑庠生春□口口鹿鸣顿首拜□子万贵暨孙□口立\n大清咸丰元年岁次辛亥三月注：此碑在王都村老寨杜氏祖茔。", "block_bbox": [375, 1082, 969, 1371], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "重修关帝庙环抱关台金妆神像碑记", "block_bbox": [378, 1446, 991, 1489], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "兹村直午，旧有关帝庙一座、献殿三间，不知创自何代。至乾隆年间，有耆老杜君讳允惠、允举，起而重修，有碑可考。历年久远，庙貌神像有风雨剥落之虞，适有耆老卫君口口侯君振福杜君口口等，目睹心惨，募化赀财八十千文，竭力董率。俾催残之景象，顿为改观；赫耀之声灵，俨乎可接。功成，属文于余。余思圣帝，忠著汉室，义结桃园，凛凛乎忠肝义胆，且令乎千载以下，顽者廉懦者立，是大有裨于名教也。至于至大至刚，气直塞乎天地；允文允武，功常炳若日星。前人之述备矣，非浅见寡闻者所以赞其万一也。然亦有不容已于一赞者，亦天籁之自鸣也。因作俚句曰：峨峨古庙赖谁修？物换星移几度秋。鸟革翬飞经后进，松苍柏翠想前猷。檐牙高啄凌河汉，台榭轩翔射斗牛。千载英灵今宛在，", "block_bbox": [290, 1506, 1185, 2405], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 12}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9794883728027344, "coordinate": [290.79693603515625, 1506.263671875, 1185.873046875, 2405.650634765625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9365056753158569, "coordinate": [290.52716064453125, 600.582763671875, 1330.3603515625, 764.592041015625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8767238855361938, "coordinate": [373.461669921875, 238.00360107421875, 905.349365234375, 403.23358154296875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8707234263420105, "coordinate": [293.67425537109375, 963.834228515625, 1329.19921875, 1064.926025390625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.848759651184082, "coordinate": [374.79364013671875, 782.2429809570312, 907.9669799804688, 823.2546997070312]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7581124305725098, "coordinate": [376.281982421875, 902.1854858398438, 884.869140625, 942.7616577148438]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.7004144191741943, "coordinate": [378.5626525878906, 1446.6678466796875, 991.3258056640625, 1489.1197509765625]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.6905432939529419, "coordinate": [375.829833984375, 479.65277099609375, 545.0151977539062, 521.7930297851562]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.6887302994728088, "coordinate": [378.2290344238281, 1204.900146484375, 707.6865234375, 1244.9650