n道光陆年岁次丙戌夏月吉日立\n\n## 清故处士杜公讳金龙配氏墓\n\n寨，及杜金龙事迹等）\n\n\n\n陕郡增生□□口□口顿首拜□邑庠生春□口口鹿鸣顿首拜□子万贵暨孙□口立\n\n大清咸丰元年岁次辛亥三月注：此碑在王都村老寨杜氏祖茔。\n\n## 重修关帝庙环抱关台金妆神像碑记\n\n兹村直午，旧有关帝庙一座、献殿三间，不知创自何代。至乾隆年间，有耆老杜君讳允惠、允举，起而重修，有碑可考。历年久远，庙貌神像有风雨剥落之虞，适有耆老卫君口口侯君振福杜君口口等，目睹心惨，募化赀财八十千文，竭力董率。俾催残之景象，顿为改观；赫耀之声灵，俨乎可接。功成，属文于余。余思圣帝，忠著汉室，义结桃园，凛凛乎忠肝义胆，且令乎千载以下，顽者廉懦者立，是大有裨于名教也。至于至大至刚，气直塞乎天地；允文允武，功常炳若日星。前人之述备矣，非浅见寡闻者所以赞其万一也。然亦有不容已于一赞者，亦天籁之自鸣也。因作俚句曰：峨峨古庙赖谁修？物换星移几度秋。鸟革翬飞经后进，松苍柏翠想前猷。檐牙高啄凌河汉，台榭轩翔射斗牛。千载英灵今宛在，", "isStart": false, "isEnd": false, "images": {"imgs/img_in_image_box_1224_380_1744_2424.jpg": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//5781bcf5-6768-4bc8-a9e1-c68114fdbc50/markdown_0/imgs/img_in_image_box_1224_380_1744_2424.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A32%3A18Z%2F-1%2F%2Ffaa09d014be902130b2ff59fa42c15577441f61dc1d0c6b04a3d40be1aa02e58"}}, "outputImages": {"layout_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//5781bcf5-6768-4bc8-a9e1-c68114fdbc50/layout_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A32%3A20Z%2F-1%2F%2F878f547a849a8f37d11d77c78edcb22f1b1fb9ca9098351e758c9ce346bee175", "region_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//5781bcf5-6768-4bc8-a9e1-c68114fdbc50/region_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A32%3A20Z%2F-1%2F%2F1fadf77f6f15a288fac07ec34613096d75bd1e9edbab6b2aed8f72a50b8bf06f", "overall_ocr_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//5781bcf5-6768-4bc8-a9e1-c68114fdbc50/overall_ocr_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A32%3A20Z%2F-1%2F%2F028f023ebc02f54c6acf002270112b92671f84b203198f90812fcdec58d410c4", "layout_order_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//5781bcf5-6768-4bc8-a9e